<TITLE> Promoted college teachers posted at last </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Aug 13 (bdnews24.com)  The government has at last posted 476 associate professors of the civil service education cadre, three months after their promotion, an education ministry circular said Wednesday. The associate professors in question have been asked to join their new college posts by Aug 21, the ministry said. The teachers' appointments were delayed due to various complications after their promotions on May 13. bdnews24.c
